        "id": "ShyvanaQ",
        "name": "Emberstrike",
        "description": "Shyvana's next attack strikes both the target and the surrounding area. This Ability can be recast. While in Dragon Form, it gains an additional recast, dealing massive damage to a single target.",
        "tooltip": "<spellPassive>Passive:</spellPassive> Shyvana's Attacks deal <magicDamage>{{ calc_max_health_damage }} max Health magic damage</magicDamage> <OnHit>%i:OnHit% On-Hit</OnHit> and reduce this Ability's Cooldown by {{ cooldown_reduction }} seconds.<br /><br /><spellActive>Active:</spellActive> Shyvana's next Attack strikes the target and the surrounding area dealing <physicalDamage>{{ calc_damage }} physical damage</physicalDamage>. This Ability may be <recast>Recast</recast> after an Attack or short delay within the next {{ recastduration }} seconds.<br /><br /><keywordMajor>Dragon Form:</keywordMajor> Shyvana gains an additional <recast>Recast</recast>, causing her to bite the target of her next Attack dealing <trueDamage>{{ calc_dragon_form_damage }} true damage</trueDamage>.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}",
