        "name": "Inferno Aegis",
        "description": "Shyvana gains a shield, movement speed, and after a short delay, the area around her detonates.  While in Dragon Form, the explosion will heal her if it strikes an enemy champion.",
        "tooltip": "Shyvana wraps herself in flames for {{ duration }} seconds, gaining <shield>{{ calc_shield }} Shield</shield>, increased by <shield>{{ calc_shield_per_nearby_champion }}</shield> per nearby enemy champion and <speed>{{ movespeed }} Move Speed</speed>, increased to <speed>{{ movespeedtowardsenemies }}</speed> when moving towards enemy champions.<br /><br />When the effect ends, the <shield>Shield</shield> is broken, or upon <recast>Recast</recast> the area around her detonates, dealing <magicDamage>{{ damage }} magic damage</magicDamage>.<br /><br /><keywordMajor>Dragon Form:</keywordMajor> If the detonation hits an enemy champion Shyvana <healing>restores from {{ calc_heal_min }} to {{ calc_heal_max }} Health</healing> based on her missing Health.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}",
