        "name": "Dragon's Descent",
        "description": "Shyvana transforms into a Dragon and leaps forward causing enemies along her path to flee. While in Dragon form she becomes larger and her basic abilities are empowered.",
        "tooltip": "<spellPassive>Passive</spellPassive>: Shyvana generates <keywordMajor>{{ fury_generation }} Dragon Fury</keywordMajor> by striking enemies with Attacks and Abilities, increased by {{ tt_fury_mult }} while in <keywordMajor>Dragon Form</keywordMajor>, and reduced {{ tt_fury_aoe_penalty }} by when striking in an area against non-champions.<br /><br /><spellActive>Active</spellActive>: Shyvana transforms into her <keywordMajor>Dragon Form</keywordMajor>, becoming <attention>Unstoppable</attention>, and flying to the target location breathing fire on enemies below dealing <magicDamage>{{ damage }} magic damage</magicDamage> and causing them <status>Flee for {{ fearduration }} seconds</status>.<br /><br />While transformed, Shyvana's basic Abilities are upgraded, she gains <scaleHealth>{{ calc_bonus_health }} bonus Health</scaleHealth>, size, and Attack Range. Shyvana loses <keywordMajor>Dragon Fury</keywordMajor> over time and her transformation ends when she has no <keywordMajor>Dragon Fury</keywordMajor> remaining.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}",
